    mknutsen.aiproject.game
    game is a set of classes that directly involve the playing of the game.
    mknutsen.aiproject.player
    Player package handles creating the abstract player and implementing it for use with a mouse and keyboard.
    mknutsen.aiproject.player.ai
    the AI package has the basis for any AI player as well as a small player that can be used to test individual procedures.
    mknutsen.aiproject.player.ai.decisiontree
    the decision tree package has the components for a decision tree including the abstract basis for one and two implementations.
